# .dev.vars — Cloudflare Workers local-dev environment variables
# Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored) for local Wrangler development.
# These are LOADED ONLY by `wrangler dev` (i.e. `npm run dev:workers`).
# For plain `npm run dev` (Vite + Hydrogen), use .env.local instead.

# ============================================================================
# Required: Shopify Storefront API
# ============================================================================

